{
  "title": "148863991.the Long Way Round",
  "slug": "148863991the-long-way-round",
  "publishedAt": "2025-11-30T19:30:11.067Z",
  "excerpt": "Upon graduating from college, I didn’t really know what I wanted to do next.",
  "image": "",
  "readTime": "2 min",
  "content": [
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Upon graduating from college, I didn’t really know what I wanted to do next.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "I knew I was interested in psychology - my then major - but not enough to pursue a master’s degree.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "I also knew that I had a wealth of other interests - including marketing, teaching, writing, entrepreneurship, and cooking - and thought I’d explore",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "those",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "options before committing to something long-term.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Long story short:",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "that’s not what happened.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Instead, I took a different path. I ended up working for five years in a combination food & beverage and retail jobs.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "I could tell you this wasn’t the best of decisions, given how lots of folks and friends my age ended up in much high-paying jobs (and likely have even",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "higher",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "paying jobs today).",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "I could also tell you that I regret the path I took.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "But, the fact is,",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "I don’t",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": ".",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Working in retail taught me many valuable lessons, and it’s made me a better person because of it.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "It taught me about a dozen transferable skills — skills that hard to teach.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "I also learned about sales and product marketing. About what makes people tick and what compels them to buy.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Best of all, I now get to say I have a 'combined 5 years of experience in espresso-based beverage-making, premium tea selling, and specialty-food merchandising'--because",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "I do",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": ".",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "It's taken a long time to acknowledge it, and great deal of",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "listening",
          "marks": [
            "link-0"
          ]
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "to what other people have",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "had to say",
          "marks": [
            "link-1"
          ]
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "on the subject, but I'm now convinced--",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "absolutely",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "--that having more experience and more exposure to",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "other",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "roles in",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "other",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "industries is an asset,",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "not",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "a liability.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ],
